Introduction

Bang Jeemin is a South Korean dancer and singer under WAKEONE.

She first debuted as a child actress in 2013 in the drama "All About My Romance". She played in a total of four dramas until 2015.

From June to September 2023, Bang Jeemin participated in HYBE and Belift Lab's survival show R U Next?, where she ranked 4th place in the final, but was unable to debut as she wasn't chosen by the producers.

In 2024, she was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she ended up ranking 2nd place in the final with 591,495 votes, thus securing her spot as a member of the final group, izna.

Bang Jeemin made her debut with the group on November 25, 2024, with the release of their first mini album titled "N/a".
